snippet: Cappie Pondexter scored a season-high 21 points to help the Liberty end a three-game losing streak with an 81-64 victory over the visiting Washington Mystics.
lead_paragraph: Cappie Pondexter scored a season-high 21 points to help the Liberty end a three-game losing streak with an 81-64 victory over the visiting Washington Mystics.

headline.main: Pondexter Leads Liberty in Rout of Mystics
